you fucking asshole!

16:02.428 --> 16:03.987
Look, I'll pay you
whatever you want.

16:04.063 --> 16:06.692
Oh, you'll pay!
Oh, hell, yes, you'll pay!

16:06.765 --> 16:09.667
You live in that huge mansion
with your fancy jet planes!

16:09.735 --> 16:10.896
Oh, you'll pay!

16:10.970 --> 16:12.836
And you will never see this girl
or her baby ever again!

16:12.905 --> 16:14.669
Mom! Please!

16:14.740 --> 16:16.800
