Don't go!

16:36.028 --> 16:37.496
Sweetie...

16:37.563 --> 16:40.192
Sweetie, he is not worth it.

16:40.265 --> 16:41.995
We'll have the baby
if you want.

16:42.067 --> 16:43.501
I'll raise it as mine.

16:43.569 --> 16:45.128
We're gonna make it work.

16:45.204 --> 16:47.173
I promise you.
All right?

16:47.239 --> 16:49.470
