16:49.541 --> 16:51.339
We're gonna be okay.

16:51.410 --> 16:52.742
Dyah!

16:52.811 --> 16:53.870
Wow!

16:53.946 --> 16:54.777
Just...wow!

16:57.016 --> 17:00.009
I see why Samantha stayed out
of Darrin's business now.

17:00.085 --> 17:03.078
I so did not need
to see that.

17:05.790 --> 17:07.349
I'm off the case.

17:07.425 --> 17:09.588
You and me both, partner.

17:09.661 --> 17:12.858
Yeah, I slipped over to that
dame's joint to question her...

17:12.931 --> 17:14.194
and things got hot.

17:14.266 --> 17:15.097
What did she say?

17:15.166 --> 17:16.657
Say?
Nothing.

17:16.734 --> 17:19.432
But she did things to me that
I didn't think were possible.

17:19.505 --> 17:21.201
That looker ran me
through the yard

17:21.272 --> 17:22.297
