be the same.

17:33.552 --> 17:34.645
Because of sex.

17:34.720 --> 17:36.245
You don't know
the half of it.

17:36.321 --> 17:37.812
And I have you to thank.

17:37.890 --> 17:39.859
And Dermott's
super-hot sister,

17:39.925 --> 17:41.518
and this old key and --

17:41.593 --> 17:42.993
Hank? Hank?!

17:43.062 --> 17:45.156
