what you want to save,

18:13.292 --> 18:14.225
just how far back
you want to forget.

18:14.293 --> 18:15.192
Sorry, tiger.

18:15.260 --> 18:19.197
Maybe I can live with sleeping
with my dad's old girlfriend

18:19.264 --> 18:21.028
